      In India, you can call **Vandrevala Foundation Helpline: 1860 266 2345**.
    </template>
  </category>

  <category>
    <pattern>I FEEL HOPELESS</pattern>
    <template>
      I'm here for you. ðŸ’™ Please reach out to someone who can help.
      You are **strong** and **loved**. If you need urgent help, please contact a helpline.
